winds at force of 8 to 9, heavy snow squalls.

1057
01:14:18,391 --> 01:14:20,242
你听见Bangs说什么了
You heard Bangs on the radio!

1058
01:14:20,267 --> 01:14:24,231
我们没有罗盘 也没法联络
We have no compass! we have no way to communicate!

1059
01:14:26,781 --> 01:14:31,531
